
This directory contains the following :

readme	-- 	this file
Doc		-- 	directory containing documentation
c2pro	-- 	directory containig prolog sources for a translator
	   		that scans C header files and ouputs prolog specs.
	   		(see Doc/ctrans.doc for details)
pro2c	--	directory containing prolog sources for an interface
			generator that reads the prolog specification output
			by translator in c2pro and outputs C code containing
			the foreign interface definitions for functions, constants
			and C structures. (see Doc/intfgen.doc for details)
deps	--	makefile dependency generator
